A bustling indoor Asian market at night, rendered in Studio Ghibli style with warm golden lighting and soft watercolor textures. Countless tiny vendor stalls stacked vertically across multiple floors, draped with colorful silk fabrics in crimson, jade, and gold cascading like waterfalls. A lone Western traveler with an umbrella tucked under his arm stands in the crowded aisle, surrounded by animated vendors gesturing enthusiastically from their compact booths. Calculators and merchandise spill from every corner. The atmosphere is chaotic yet magical, with dust motes floating in shafts of warm light, steam rising from nearby food stalls, and the sense of a thousand small negotiations happening simultaneously. Perspective looking upward through the atrium reveals floor after floor of identical tiny shops disappearing into a dreamy haze above.
